title: JAN 27 2022 - POLL REVEALS ONLY 31% WANT U.S. TROOPS TO DEFEND UKRAINE
description:
A new national survey by Rasmussen reveals that only 31% of Americans want U.S. troops deployed to defend Ukraine, liberal supreme court Justice Stephen Breyer announced his retirement, U.S. State Department personnel in China are asking for permission to leave amidst concerns over household separation and covid, plus we have to dive into Senator Johnson’s opposition to family policies and why it’s a mistake for the conservative movement.

Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
